<module>
    <h>dubh</h>
    <p><g>dubh</g>
        <en>black</en> is a <a href="?xx=adjectives/simple_adjectives">simple adjective</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-predicate">
            <h>predicate</h>
            <p><g>dubh</g> can be used as the predicate of the verb <a href="?gd=bi"
                ><g>bi</g></a>.</p>
            <p>Examples with an animal subject – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha an cù dubh.</gd>
                        <tr>The dog is black.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="uses-mod">
            <h>modifier</h>
            <p><g>dubh</g> can be used to modify a <a href="?xx=nouns/common_nouns">common noun</a> –
            <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha an <m>cù dubh</m> aig an dorus.</gd>
                    <tr>The black dog is at the door.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
        
    </section>

</module>
